{
  "text": "Host-based cyber defence is mainly relied on Anti-Virus (AV) and end-point security solutions installed on the host machines, which scans for known virus signatures or detect and limit malicious behaviours [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] . Banking Trojans are using different techniques to install themselves on a host while remain undetected as follow.",
